data.description: What a view! Spend your evenings on the back porch watching the Fountain in the Pond while barbecuing with your guests. This wonderfully maintained home has beautiful hardwood floors with Fireplace and a wonderful wall of windows for natural light. The circular floor plan from living to kitchen and formal dining back to living room allows for a great flow when entertaining guests. Oversized Master ensuite can easily accommodate larger king sized furniture with a separate door transitioning into the Master bath which features a tub and stand alone shower with separate vanities and connects into the Master closet. Each of the 2nd and 3rd bedrooms has a full bath! The large oversized 2.5 car garage will give you plenty of space for storage or workbench for your handyman projects. Off the front entry of the home you will find a fantastic space for your work from home office or hobby room to the right and formal dining to the left. All this just minutes from retail shopping, theatres and turnpike access for a quick commute. Seller is offering up to $5000 towards buyers rate buy down or closing costs.
